{"tid":2121182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★播毒？】市民硬闖泳灘 用鄰近廁所洗手盆洗頭、沖腳 兼留下的內褲","createTime":"2020-07-23T07:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T05:10:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"299b8de87d9918d50e27f93fad8ee49486917963","tid":2121182,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"康文署宣布關閉泳灘後，泳灘設置的更衣室及戶外沖身設施同步暫停，惟市民硬闖，亦使泳灘衛生狀況更形惡劣。泳灘關閉設施，泳客反而利用鄰近廁所更衣、沖身，用洗手盆洗頭、沖腳，本來非用作泳灘用途的洗手間地板亦積滿泥沙。《香港01》記者在鄰近淺水灣的廁所內更發現疑似泳客留下的內褲。第三波疫情之下香港人人自危，但泳灘的衛生狀況，卻比關閉之前更加令擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/501169/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%81%E7%81%98-%E9%9B%A3%E6%95%B5%E6%B3%B3%E5%AE%A2%E7%86%B1%E6%83%85%E5%97%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E8%25A7%2580%25E9%25BB%259E%2F501169%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%2581%2598-%25E9%259B%25A3%25E6%2595%25B5%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E7%2586%25B1%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%2597%258E&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=6c9ea3a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E/501169/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%81%E7%81%98-%E9%9B%A3%E6%95%B5%E6%B3%B3%E5%AE%A2%E7%86%B1%E6%83%85%E5%97%8E</a>"},{"pid":"07dde12234d6740f3e6b399cca304539036cd53a","tid":2121182,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200722/362634947317600256.jpeg/3cxElU-vF04HWBNpxu5D9U8_pjSH7-39NnNynDZzcpw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200722%2F362634947317600256.jpeg%2F3cxElU-vF04HWBNpxu5D9U8_pjSH7-39NnNynDZzcpw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5d93b0bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45f62f56378066b5c80de66b1bf48573c26038fb","tid":2121182,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime